### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Initiate Payment - Success
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-REST-001",
  "senderId": "user1",
  "receiverId": "user2",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Get Payment Status
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/payments/TXN-REST-001/status

### Get Transaction History
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/payments/user/user1

### Get Ledger History
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/ledger/user/user1

### Initiate Payment - Insufficient Funds
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-REST-002",
  "senderId": "user1",
  "receiverId": "user2",
  "amount": 999999.00,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Initiate Payment - Duplicate (Idempotency Test)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-REST-003",
  "senderId": "user1",
  "receiverId": "user2",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Initiate Payment - Duplicate Again (same transactionId)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-REST-003",
  "senderId": "user1",
  "receiverId": "user2",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Initiate Payment - Validation Error (negative amount)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-REST-004",
  "senderId": "user1",
  "receiverId": "user2",
  "amount": -100.00,
  "currency": "USD"
}

